      • taskClaimed

        public void taskClaimed(org.jbpm.task.event.entity.TaskUserEvent event)
        This event is triggered when a task is assigned to a user, OR when a task that is directly assigned to the user is first created. When the task is directly assigned, it DOES NOT trigger a TaskCreated event.
        Specified by:

        public void taskStarted(org.jbpm.task.event.entity.TaskUserEvent event)
